// Canonical 5-phase tick pipeline for the Serial (CPU) backend:
//
//   1. Mask build  — fill_all() populates MaskBuffer + TargetMask
//   2. Policy eval — backend.evaluate() writes actions into scratch
//   3. Shuffle     — Fisher-Yates over action indices keyed by (seed, tick)
//   4. Apply + cascade — emit root events, run cascade fixed-point
//   5. View fold   — fold this tick's events into ViewRegistry
//   6. Tick advance

